<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.tonyfoale.com/Articles/Balance/BALANCE.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.tonyfoale.com/Articles/Balance/BALANCE.htm" rel="nofollow">Balance and Steering</a>, by <a href="/w/index.php?title=Tony_Foale&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Tony Foale (page does not exist)">Tony Foale</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.virginiawind.com/tips/steering.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.virginiawind.com/tips/steering.asp" rel="nofollow">"Steering"</a> (By Mike Howell)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.superbikeschool.com/machinery/no-bs-machine.php" class="external text" title="http://www.superbikeschool.com/machinery/no-bs-machine.php" rel="nofollow">"No B.S. Machine"</a> physical experimentation</li>
<li><a href="http://www.rattlebars.com/valkfaq/tirewear/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.rattlebars.com/valkfaq/tirewear/index.html" rel="nofollow">"Motorcycle Tire Wear"</a> Inserted by and with permission of the author</li>
<li><a href="http://www.losethetrainingwheels.org/default.aspx?Lev=2&amp;ID=36" class="external text" title="http://www.losethetrainingwheels.org/default.aspx?Lev=2&amp;ID=36" rel="nofollow">"Counter-Intuitive"</a> (see Rocket Bike) relevant physical experimentation proving that turning bars to left cause bike to turn to the right</li>
</ul>


